\item {\bf{Step 5:}} Making a Decision and interpreting the Results of the Test

Since the test statistic is greater than the t-critical value ($4.41 > 2.01$), we reject the null hypothesis.  Thus we can say that there is a strong, positive relationship  between male height and male self estemm.

\end{itemize}

 
